description: Heliospectra AB engages in the provision of lighting technology for plant research and greenhouse cultivation. The company is headquartered in Goeteborg, Vastra Gotalands and currently employs 31 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2014-06-18. The company is also used for research purposes, including plant development and phytoceutical development as well as in physiology, biochemistry, molecular biology and entomology of plants. The Heliospectra AB's LED products have six to eight adjustable wavelength groups from near UV to far-red. The Heliospectra's system can reduce energy consumption by up to 50% in greenhouse industry and improve crop quality.
